wsdl:operation.name: GetPersonIDByMemberNumber
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve a person ID by passing a hyphenated member number. Returns zero if no match.

wsdl:operation.name: GetOfficeDefinitions
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Retrieve a list of all office definitions.

wsdl:operation.name: GetOfficerRecord
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Supply an officer id and get back an officer record for the officer ID provided.

wsdl:operation.name: GetOfficerRecordsChangedSince
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Supply a change since date and get back a collection of officer records changed since that date.

wsdl:operation.name: GetAllOfficesForPerson
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Supply a person ID and get back a collection of all current and previous offices for that person.

wsdl:operation.name: AddUpdateMemberCredentials
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Supply person id an updated credential set and get back results. This method will return a success flag as well as an add/update indicator if the credentials were 'Updated' or 'Created'. If the success flag is false, the reason will be provided in the error reason return parameter.

wsdl:operation.name: ValidateMemberByCredentials
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Supply a user name and password to this method. The method will return a zero for no matching records and a greater than zero number representing the person ID of the matching member.

wsdl:operation.name: GetOPCalendarEntries
